\({\cal D} = \{(x_1, y_1), (x_2, y_2), ..., (x_n, y_n)\}\)

  • \(\rho\) \[ r = \frac{\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i - \bar{x})(y_i - \bar{y})}{\sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i - \bar{x})^2 \sum_{i=1}^n (y_i - \bar{y})^2}} \]

  • \(H_0: \rho = 0\) \[ t = \frac{\sqrt{n-2}\cdot r}{\sqrt{1 - r^2}} \stackrel{H_0\text{ }}{\sim} t(n-2) \]

\[ y = f(\boldsymbol{x}) + \epsilon,\quad \epsilon\sim \bullet (0, \sigma^2) \]

  • \(y\): (output), (target)

    • \(\boldsymbol x\)

    • : (dependent variable), (response variable)

  • \(\boldsymbol x\): (input), (feature), (attribute)

    • \(y\)

    • : (independent variable), (explanatory variable), (predictor), (covariate)

\[ f(\boldsymbol{x}|\boldsymbol{w}) = w_0 + w_1 x_1 + w_2 x_2 + \cdots + w_d x_d \]

  • , \(\boldsymbol{x}\)


() \[ {\cal D} = \{(\boldsymbol{x}_i, y_i)\in\mathbb{R}^d\times\mathbb{R}\,|\, i = 1, 2, ..., n\} \]


  • : \(\tilde{y}_i = f(\boldsymbol{x}_i|\boldsymbol{w})\), \(i = 1, 2, ..., n\)

  • : training error . \(\boldsymbol{w} = (w_0, w_1, ..., w_d)^\top\) \[ {\cal L}(\boldsymbol{w}) = \frac{1}{2}\sum_{i=1}^n (y_i - \tilde{y}_i)^2 = \frac{1}{2}\sum_{i=1}^n \left\{y_i - f(\boldsymbol{x}_i|\boldsymbol{w})\right\}^2 \]

  • Residual Sum of Squares(RSS) (least squares method)


Measures of Fit: \(R^2\)

  • \(y\) \(\boldsymbol{x}\) \(\epsilon\)

  • \(y\) \(\epsilon\) \(\boldsymbol{x}\) ( )

    • \(y\) : \({\sf SST} = \sum_{i=1}^n(y_i-\bar{y})^2\)

    • \(\epsilon\) : \({\sf RSS} = \sum_{i=1}^n(y_i-\tilde{y}_i)^2\)

    • \(\boldsymbol{x}\) : \({\sf SST} - {\sf RSS}\)

  • \(R^2\) \(y\) \(\boldsymbol{x}\) \[ R^2 = \frac{{\sf SST} - {\sf RSS}}{{\sf SST}} = 1 - \frac{{\sf RSS}} {{\sf SST}} \]

  • gen.data <- function(N, SD, w0, w1) 
{
  x <- runif(N, min = -5, max = 5)
  y <- w0 + w1*x + rnorm(N, sd = SD)

  return(data.frame(x = x, y = y))
}

panel.cor <- function(x, y, digits = 2, prefix = "", cex.cor, ...)
{
    par(usr = c(0, 1, 0, 1))
    r <- abs(cor(x, y))
    txt <- format(c(r, 0.123456789), digits = digits)[1]
    txt <- paste0(prefix, txt)
    if(missing(cex.cor)) cex.cor <- 0.8/strwidth(txt)
    text(0.5, 0.5, txt, cex = cex.cor * r)
}

pairs(adv[,-1], lower.panel = panel.smooth, upper.panel = panel.cor)
